ひとつだけ小さいなパンチので…
by Humble amateur » Sat 04.04.2009 8:26 am It might be too early for me considering my current ability to speak Japanese, but I really wanted to give it a try. Only one little punch and she's already at her limit?ひとつだけ小さいなパンチので、彼女はもう自分の限界である？
