by Humble amateur » Sat 04.04.2009 9:01 am becki_kanou wrote:Are you talking about punch, like a punch to the face, or punch like an alchoholic drink?Also, did you run that through a machine-translator? It sounds suspiciously babelfishy. (Forgive me if you didn't.)A punch to the face with a bare fist. No, I don't run anything through translator machines. Sorry if it's that bad... Humble amateur
