Re: ひとつだけ小さいなパンチので…
by kurisuto » Sat 04.04.2009 9:24 am （小さい）パンチ一発だけで彼女はもう限界だ？発 is the right counter for punches. Now, I put "chiisai" (by the way, it's either "chiisai" without -na or "chiisana" without "i") in parentheses because it doesn't sound natural to me in this instance, but it may be fine.　自分 is not necessary, and you can omit "no" in "node" (anyways it would have been "na node").
kurisuto
